{
  "stem": "6719.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then there were Vorarbeiters, which means-- wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What the hell is a Vorarbeiter?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That, again, delegated people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like a hierarchy from there to here to there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But lo and behold, where all of us had a-- two triangles, a red and a yellow, next to our number, he had a green one on there, a green and a yellow.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we know-- or knew immediately that he's of the-- let's say, he's a criminal, as we used to call them, OK?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, his name was Hans Schorr-- S-- he is not alive, so his name is really not important-- S-C-H-O-R or S-C-H-O-R-R.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Hans Schorr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was a real short stop, very wiry, very loud.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He used to use his stick a lot, tattooing you on the head or this and that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But in-- and on the whole, he wasn't a bad guy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was just a nut.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, uh, he got some of us together that spoke his language.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were-- let me see, now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was [GERMAN], [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Adi ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Wolfe ?], myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's three.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I think there was a fourth one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "No, the other two were German boys-- that spoke the language and were in Kanada.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he got us all together and said, OK, this is Hans' law.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, when you find something that you can pocket in your hand, and it's gold, I want it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you don't, they said, I'm going to rip your neck off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day, a transport came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think-- I believe that transport came from Holland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was in 1943, when I was still working down there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
